{"tid":1807002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"綠曱甴濫捕你係咪好嬲? 可以點做?","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:02:27.000Z","uid":186361,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"136afb79254f21c805692b4fedc8d444f9729fd5","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"我地成日講既口號<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人報仇</strong></span>係點樣做到?<br />\n<br />\n香港個問題出現係個<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">制度</span></strong>啊<br />\n我地要做既係<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2020推動真雙普選</span></span></span></strong><br />\n而呢樣野先可以真真正正幫到義士 手足等緊我地嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>美國人權法</strong></span></span>都講明香港再玩小圈子就會制裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>而2020係最後機會</strong></span></span><br />\n貿易戰令中國元氣大傷仲有債券到期要還 大量企業支爆 對美金渴求令中國必須依靠香港而全球反共潮中 仲有二年後換哂身份證 人臉識別再運行 我地叫口號都俾人拉啊! <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>終國根本冇能力去同人拗數</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有你覺得港共唔會秋後算帳?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2019</span></span>入邊黑警日日濫捕打人冇責任再被表揚<br />\n建制狗落選再派公職<br />\n議員被DQ<br />\n雷射筆變攻擊性武器 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港法治已死</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地黎緊發夢既口號可唔可以係:</span><br />\n#光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#取消功能組別 我要真普選</span><br />\n#驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有人識整文宣真係幫幫手俾文宣組啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該哂<br />\n如果你唔明點解要咁做 你可以上FB search 2020雙普選 大把文章可以了解<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地一定要成功 到時班狗只會變condom</strong></span></span>  手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMe2Puq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMe2Puq.jpg&h=31eaef3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWyfp21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWyfp21.jpg&h=439a4a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCEVp22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCEVp22.jpg&h=d509932b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a017832a3d7dbbcfb7e7d239c447fc35b5011e3","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n32WT0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn32WT0J.jpg&h=274fb769&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3be0e3d3afd85069753286dbbdc6badb7cf6938c","tid":1807002,"uid":238432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"568e82b64ac97b3eec0d35088dfc82bd9bee47a9","tid":1807002,"uid":238432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"b842120930cd8a722cb35a57f96ee826dc14cfc0","tid":1807002,"uid":238432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"b9e6dd4d161a5ec94c327f0a2d097754f73c2c3c","tid":1807002,"uid":238432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"34ca755d65d304bfb198e1cb3bfb0d1bbc745256","tid":1807002,"uid"