:00.000Z","msg":"人權法咪用黎制裁香港個撚屌廢官<br />\n沒收呢班撚樣既資產。 <br />\n<br />\n得閒download twitter 同一個叫 @Solomon Yue講話香港人要2020普選立法會。<br />\n<br />\nFB search 2020 普選立法會 <br />\n俾少少時間睇睇增長知識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8886e8d2c6eb7ebbe8193f6417f26f047492a9","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4f209408a9b3ce46140f0b40f0731819b489469e","tid":1807002,"uid":14941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"警方新策略, 開始當埋和理非係共犯了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"要停止香港呢場戰爭只有唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2020普選立法會<br />\n取消功能組別<br />\n我要真普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好再俾制度撚。"},{"pid":"386c486996f85e8d768641af712b3479bf0440da","tid":1807002,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ff9ebc6d521d30c7c33f0d77ec143bdf654bac","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfa9uLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdfa9uLx.jpg&h=d97ad07d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc3d624479d543027a25d827e8ba7719047c9b2c","tid":1807002,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ee7ef0b904706dad25f3d0855ece7cff74dfb4","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjuN0Up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjuN0Up.jpg&h=9e84244e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">我要真普選</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"89145d5b9148b8d3bd3eab341a4562db656e35e8","tid":1807002,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"2020普選立法會<br />\n取消功能組別<br />\n我要真普選"},{"pid":"58d4ad6126fcf601b10831875d1abdb55716204a","tid":1807002,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"長期戰線文宣有寫<br />\n<br />\n黑警打份工，佢地最驚係失業，佢濫捕，私刑，無跟正常程序做野，你大條道理投訴，報警，等佢地鬼打鬼，有無效都煩到佢地仆街<br />\n<br />\n你叫人唔好去，話無用，同你唔選立法會功能組別一樣咁on9...除非你一下可以打破現有制度<br />\n<br />\n要懶清高就只變縱容，相反戰線多從來無蝕底<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下，擺明被濫捕起碼有成千人，你地一齊去投訴班popo，中間有違法行為你就去報案，幾個一齊再揾埋議員律師一齊去<br />\n<br />\n黑警拉你口罩，搶走左就係偷竊，你就去報案，有片有相叫班黑警自己查，你一蚊都唔洗比<br />\n<br />\n你日日打電話去追佢地調查進度，錄哂音，呢個係你嘅權利，佢唔做野，組織苦主聯盟，叫泛民開記招，錄音放上網，去私人刑事檢控，點都好過要班義務律師四圍揾人保䆁你，咁班popo先識驚<br />\n<br />\n呢招煩鳩你，咪就係鄧小強用緊囉"},{"pid":"02c7b49fde87a60ddd57df362689e281f8fafa9c","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"2020普選立法會<br />\n取消功能組別<br />\n我要真普選"},{"pid":"208db8037f9fcb67b8632b3a73a056537cd90be4","tid":1807002,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"2020年好撚關鍵 <br />\n人權法推真普選一定要成功"},{"pid":"b9f6f39b473a6c40e52fb4121df8eab639415542","tid":1807002,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f07fac4d45f4d172ab66ffb548befc04a61db7e0","tid":1807002,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f113459dca5213d89cb08933adcadebb97a55c05","tid":1807002,"uid":160102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"諗下點解朱經緯告得入？<br />\n<br />\n因為受害人死咬唔放，即使自己告上法庭都在所不惜<br />\n<br />\n被濫捕後根本一定要咁做，咪怕煩"},{"pid":"50cea77bdb685a98976b73af4c49c91fc459a3e6","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0