lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要叫到泛民開記招先得嫁 咁易請得郁嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如專心打國際戰線啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"問題係你已被濫捕，係咪都被告啦<br />\n夠人多，泛民先會做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"7個月以黎我地已經好多手足被人拉 <br />\n除左星火積極協助 泛民真係冇做野嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如日日去佢地fb page 問佢地訓醒未 由其係大律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc26a74a495391335de46cf445d62022d6f40fd0","tid":1807002,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294b850114a5c1ad1cb1bb46249954ea240c0ebf","tid":1807002,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"美國個制裁名單又要等報告又盛<br />\n有排都未發揮到效果<br />\n所以佢地完全唔驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"有港共官員真係入唔到境嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />背後好多野我地唔知姐<br />\n但你諗深一層<br />\n我地唔帶呢個風向點幫被捕手足?<br />\n真係有用嫁 2020最後機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2020普選立法會<br />\n取消功能組別<br />\n我要真普選</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6804543a230fb0719e1770c9c7731616a9f06c2b","tid":1807002,"uid":154433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"c3fe14c548193c8fe